@mingyumkim93 Your query syntax should be according the sql database you are using. 
For example I am using postgres as source in superset, so I have to use "ending_date" - "starting_date" in custom sql in metric field, also columns should be of date type. Below is one screenshot. 

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/31547162/70904700-04d3ee00-2028-11ea-9b54-4f92b18e29f9.png)

